SIEM integration -> In our infrastructer we were configured all logs in single log account under the control tower landing zone
setup.
We were pushing all the logs in to it and we were integrated all the logs with Wazuh (SIEM tool) with IAM role,
it will will pull the logs and analyse it and if anything suspecius found, it trigger a mail to just in Jira.
Based on investigation we fix the vulnerable action items.
